constellations_other.name: Raemar, rap and reality TV
constellations_other.description: James Turrell's immersive artworks have an unusual connection with Saturday Night Live, hip hop and reality TV royalty.

results.description: Kendall Jenner welcomes Architecture Digest for a tour of her serene LA home. Just off the entry, a signature James Turrell ovoid wall sculpture greets visitors with a dreamy chromatic display, the first of many personal artistic accents woven throughout her home.

results.title_for_label: Apple and Google stores suspend Parler app
results.description: After Trump was banned permanently from Twitter and Facebook in early 2021, many supporters of the alt-right movement (including controversial group The Proud Boys) began to use an alternative app called Parler. Google and Apple removed the app from their stores for inciting violence.
